\m \wj \+w En|strong="G1722"\+w* \+w tu|strong="G4771"\+w* descendencia serán benditas \+w todas|strong="G3956"\+w* \+w las|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w familias|strong="G3965"\+w* \+w de|strong="G1722"\+w* \+w la|strong="G3588"\+w* \+w tierra|strong="G1093"\+w*. \wj*   
